# Python Administrative Utility Script

## ğŸ“Œ Overview
This project is a Python-based administrative utility script designed to perform common system administration tasks. It provides a simple menu-driven interface that allows users to retrieve system information, monitor disk usage, view running processes, back up directories, and clean temporary files.

This script is intended for students and beginners learning Python scripting for IT and system administration purposes.

---

## ğŸ›  Features
- Display system information (OS, CPU, RAM)
- Check disk usage across partitions
- View top running processes
- Back up a directory into a ZIP file
- Clean temporary files
- Menu-based user interaction

